Joy Signal, an industry leader in design and manufacture of high-density custom electronic connectors and wire harnesses supplies customers in medical, computer, electronic, communications, audio, security, and gaming industries. 
Operating in Chico for 30 years, the company is growing strongly, fueled by the global demand for increased communication and data transmission. Artificial Intelligence, Video Communication, Cloud Services, Autonomous things, and 5G are all creating high demand for the companyâ€™s custom products. 
We are looking for entry level employees willing to try their hand at a career in electronic assembly. This position requires following written instructions to assemble high density custom electronic connectors. We are looking for candidates with a strong attention to detail and strong dexterity. 
