Job Duties: 
Cut, strip, prep, crimp, solder, weld, mold, harness, plug, house, heat stamp, heat shrink, cable tie, label, test, bag. 
Read and follow basic written instructions 
Execute required production operations. 
Use machinery and equipment, as required, to perform production operations. 
Assists in training other team members and assist in defining written production processes 
Document work performed 
Have a commitment to learning and adhering to Quality standards. 
Observe safety rules and regulations. 
Must exhibit the willingness to expand job knowledge in order to keep current with changing production needs, and to enhance future promotional considerations. 
Other tasks as assigned by management 
